<p>She has continued her career in the private sector since graduating from Bilkent Industrial Engineering in 2011. For nearly 15 years, she has provided consultancy and team leadership in digital transformation and e-commerce for many corporate firms in Turkey and abroad. Alongside her corporate career, she has worked as a project manager at Sabancı Volunteers, program coordinator at Değiştiren Adımlar Association, and founding member of Açık Açık Association. While continuing her volunteer activities with Sen de Gel, she continues to provide consultancy in e-commerce abroad.</p>